sentences.sentence: See also: swimming pools in dumpsters.

sentences.sentence: JG: in downtown Chicago and other cities, coyotes and other wildlife have been found digging through dumpsters in the subway and inside supermarkets.
sentences.translation: 格：在芝加哥以及其他一些城市的市中心，人们发现地铁、超市的垃圾桶被土狼等野生动物挖穿。
